@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jdrens(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.16 + wp.cos((v2 + 0.76 / v2 + 0.95)))
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.56) * (tmp + 0.61 + tmp + 0.98)))
    v1 = ((tmp * tmp) - v0)
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
